metadata.description: Continuous territorial conquests have lead to the separation of Japan’s once unified nation. 200 of the greatest Shogun fled the capital in search for new samurai, craftsman and merchants to join their side in battle. However, the cats of foreign lands do not bow down to ANY leader. Each Shogun must prove their $HONOUR if they plan on recruiting for their clan. The battle awaits…but for now, practice your swordsmanship, sharpen your blades, and stockpile whatever you can get your paws on. Only the greatest of Shogun will come out on top. So tell me samurai… do YOU have what it takes to become the greatest Shogun?
